    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、あけまして\nおめでとうございます！\n\n急な生放送で驚きましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.0000001371,
      "endTime": 8.6000000953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "kana達、これから新曲の\nMV撮影があってね\nせっかくだから、みんなに\n新年の挨拶をしようかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8000002324,
      "endTime": 17.233330663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "昨年は、ⅢX一同\n大変お世話になりました\n本年も、何卒よろしく\nお願いいたします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3373442749,
      "endTime": 26.1440106808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、franちゃんと\nmihoちゃんはお休み中\nリフレッシュ出来た？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4440106808,
      "endTime": 31.4066664059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ\n私はハワイで過ごしたわ\nカカアコのウォールアートが\n好きで、見に行ったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.7373442429,
      "endTime": 37.9954850612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "私は、久しぶりに実家で\nゆっくり過ごしたわ。それと\nご無沙汰していた友人の\nご家族に、挨拶に行ったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3954850612,
      "endTime": 46.3702454664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "そういうkanaは\nどうだったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7369121331,
      "endTime": 48.924984742999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "お、聞いちゃう？\nkanaも海外に行ったんだ\n\nでも詳しい内容は、近々\nアップする動画を観てみてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1183180669,
      "endTime": 57.9545307873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、これからも\n『ⅢX公式ch』に注目だよ\nチャンネル登録、高評価\nよろしくお願いしま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2878642577,
      "endTime": 67.2725966214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "……あー、終わった終わった\n新年早々こいつらと仲良し\nアピールとかやってらんねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5392649511,
      "endTime": 76.7592647413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "それはこっちのセリフよ\nっていうか、わざわざ口に\n出さなくてもいいでしょ\nだからガキなのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0925980746,
      "endTime": 84.0535053114,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14140.735258699991
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "kanaが言わなくても\n貴方が大人気なく言っていた\n\nと思うけれど。まぁいいわ\n撮影に向かうわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4535053114,
      "endTime": 92.2707842369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "うわ、そういや今日の移動\nmihoの車だっけ\nあ、そうだ\n{user}が運転してよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3707883058,
      "endTime": 100.8122397919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんって\n安全運転で有名みたいだし？\n格好いいとこ\n見せて下さいよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9789064585,
      "endTime": 108.5313963114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "こいつ、たまに思い出した\nように媚び売るわね……\n撮影手伝わせた上に\nさっきまで放置してたくせに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.7647296447,
      "endTime": 117.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_02_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そうね。mihoの\n運転とか撮影に響きそうだし\n早速ですけど、今年も\nサポート、お願いしますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.5080629209,
      "endTime": 126.5912830213,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}